                    <span>One of the better books in Security, concentrating on algorithms, rather than stopping at attack descriptions. Very detailed coverage of converntional and public-key encryption. I recommend this book to anyone interested in Security and has some knowledge on algorithms.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">good book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
